MDD ta ce dubban mayakan Pakistan da ke yaki da Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD - Wani rahoto na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce sama da 'yan tawayen Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, mafi yawa suna cikin kungiyar Taliban ta Pakistan da aka haramta da alhakin kai hari kan sojoji da fararen hula na Pakistan.
Rahoton wanda aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, wacce aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta danganta da kawancen Afghanistan na kungiyar ISIS.
Wasu daga cikin mambobin TTP sun shiga cikin haɗin gwiwar IS, wanda ke da hedkwatarta a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta amsa ranar Lahadi ba game da buƙatun da Kamfanin Dillancin Labarai na Associated Press ya yi na yin sharhi.
Rahoton ya ce IS a Afghanistan, wanda aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, jami'an tsaron Afghanistan da sojojin Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wasu lokuta 'yan Taliban na Afghanistan sun yi ta kai hare-hare.
Kungiyar masu sa ido kan al'amurra da takunkumi ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ce ta shirya wannan rahoton, wanda ke bin diddigin kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda a duk fadin duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta cewa membobin IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancinta ya lalace, har yanzu IS tana cikin shugabanninta Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani dan asalin Syria.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar sa ido ta samu labarin cewa wasu manyan kwamandojin ISIS guda biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun iso Afghanistan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya kwanan nan.
"Duk da cewa a yankin ja da baya, (da ISIS) ya kasance iya kai high-profile kai hare-hare a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Har ila yau, yana nufin jawo hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da suka kulla da Amurka," in ji rahoton, wanda ke nuni da yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta kulla da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An cimma wannan yarjejeniyar ne don baiwa Amurka damar kawo karshen ayyukan da ta shafe shekaru 19 tana yi a Afghanistan, haka nan kuma kira ga Taliban da su tabbatar da cewa kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda ba za su yi amfani da yankinta ba.
Ana kuma sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta tabbatar da ba da cikakken goyon baya ga kungiyar Taliban a yakin da take yi da IS.
Bangare na biyu kuma mafi mahimmanci na yarjejeniyar ya bukaci tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da shuwagabannin siyasar Kabul.
A ranar Asabar, Ma’aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta fitar da wata sanarwa cewa ta zaman lafiya wakilin Zalmay Khalilzad aka sake rufe a cikin yankin neman tsalle fara wadannan tattaunawa, wanda aka sau da yawa dage matsayin bangarorin biyu jayayya a kan wani fursuna saki shirin.
Yarjejeniyar da Amurka ke marawa baya ta yi kira ga gwamnatin Afghanistan da ta saki fursunoni 5,000 na Taliban da Taliban don 'yantar da gwamnati da jami'an soji 1,000 a matsayin abin da ake kira kyakkyawan nufi kafin tattaunawa.
Har yanzu gwamnati tana ƙin sakin kusan fursunoni 600 na Taliban da ta kira manyan masu laifi kuma ta ba da kyauta kyauta.
Taliban sun ki.
"Jam'iyyun sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawar cikin-Afghan, mahimmin mataki na gaba don kawo karshen yakin Afghanistan na tsawon shekaru 40," in ji sanarwar Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka.
"Duk da cewa an sami gagarumin ci gaba a kan mu'amala da fursuna, to amma batun na bukatar karin kokari don magance matsalar."
A farkon makon nan ne kakakin kungiyar Taliban din ya ce a shirye yake ya gudanar da tattaunawa da shugabannin siyasar Kabul bayan hutun Musulunci na Eid al-Adha a karshen watan nan, inda ya ba da sanarwar sakin fursunan.
Wani babban abin damuwa ga Pakistan shi ne kasancewar Afghanistan na mayakan sa kai, musamman da alaka da TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda suke tare da Baluchistan Liberation Army, wanda ya dauki alhakin high-profile kai hare-hare wannan watan a kudancin Sindh lardin kazalika a kudu maso yammacin Baluchistan lardin.
