Amurka "fasa-fasa" suna riƙe da baya neman magungunan coronavirus
A duniya kokarin samar da amfani anti-Covid magunguna da ake samun cikas da Amurka saboda masu bincike suna gwajin kwayoyi a "wani sabani, Willy-nilly hanya," da gwani jagorancin Birtaniya ta shirin ya yi gargadin.
Shirin sake farfadowa na Birtaniya, wanda ya shafi marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitoci da yawa na Birtaniya, ya riga ya nuna wani sabon magani don magance cutar kuma ya nuna wasu biyu - a baya an yi tunanin cewa ba za su iya ceton rai ba - a matsayin marasa amfani.
Amma gazawar tsarin kiwon lafiya na Amurka don dacewa da wannan fitarwa yana nufin cewa sauran jiyya masu yiwuwa da za a iya share su don amfani da yawa har yanzu dole a kimanta su.
Musamman ma, convalescent plasma (jini na jini wanda ake sha daga marasa lafiya na Covid-19 kuma wanda ke dauke da garkuwar jiki wanda zai iya kare wasu daga cutar) har yanzu dole ne a gwada shi da kyau a kan babban gwajin bazuwar cutar.
Farfesa Martin Landray, daya daga cikin wadanda suka kafa shirin farfadowa da na'ura ya ce "an riga an ba dubun dubatar mutane kwayar cutar plasma a Amurka amma ba a bazuwar wadannan jiyya ba."
"Su ne kawai ba mutane convalescent jini a cikin bege shi zai yi aiki. Vast yawa da aka bai wa kuma har yanzu ba su da masaniya ko yana taimaka ko cutarwa ko ba shi da wani tasiri," ya kara da cewa Landray, wani gwani a kafa manyan sikelin-magunguna gwaji.
Amurka ta kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje, bazuwar kuma wannan ya ƙare har da samar da mummunan magani.
Gwaje-gwaje na kwayoyi na Randomised sune ma'aunin zinariya don nuna magunguna masu amfani.
Suka cire m nuna bambanci da zai girgije clinicians 'hukunce-hukunce.
Dubban mutane ana basu magani kuma wasu dubbai ana basu placebo.
Babu wanda ya san abin da aka ba su.
Sa'an nan kuma ana kwatanta sakamako da ingancin maganin da aka bayyana.
Ta wannan hanyar, farfadowa da na'ura ya iya nuna cewa steroid dexamethasone ya rage mutuwa da kashi uku a cikin marasa lafiya na Covid-19 akan na'urorin bada iska.
Hakanan ya nuna cewa magani mai yawa hydroxychloroquine - da kuma maganin hada magunguna lopinavir da ritonavir - ba su da wani tasiri wajen ceton rayukan marasa lafiya.
Musamman wadannan gwaje-gwaje da ake bukata sosai yawa na marasa lafiya da kuma babu wani guda asibiti da ya isa domin irin wannan bincike.
Birtaniya ta sami wata babbar fa'ida - a Karkasa Hukumar Kiwon Lafiya ta Kasa.
Sabanin haka, sabis na kiwon lafiya na Amurka ya lalace kuma nasarar da ya samu kawai wajen nuna yiwuwar magani yana nuna amfanin maganin remdesivir mai tsada don hanzarta dawo da wasu marasa lafiya na Covid-19.
"Akwai kuri'a da kuri'a na kananan kwayoyi da suka shafi 'yan dozin ko' yan ɗari marasa lafiya da ke faruwa a Amurka amma babu wani abu," ya kara da cewa Landray.
"Suna kasa yin manyan, bazuwar gwaji da kuma cewa ƙare sama da samar da mummunan magani. Yana sa al'adar magani poorer da sakamakon ga marasa lafiya poorer."
Landray ya ce wannan gazawar tana da matukar damuwa lokacin da aka yi amfani da plasma convalescent, wanda likitoci da yawa suka yi imanin cewa zai iya samun muhimmiyar rawar da za su taka wajen kula da marasa lafiya masu fama da cutar Covid-19.
"Idan ka dubi Amurka, an yi amfani da babbar yawa ta wannan magani a kan wani sabani Willy-nilly-akai. Birtaniya ta fi gaban awo idan aka kwatanta da abin da ke faruwa a can," ya kara da cewa.
Farfesa Peter Horby, wani masani kan cututtuka masu yaduwa da sauran wanda ya kafa shirin farfadowa da na'ura, ya ce: "An sami rahotanni na marasa lafiya 20,000 da ke samun convalescent plasma a cikin gungu amma babu wani daga cikin waɗannan marasa lafiya da aka bazuwar.
Idan da sun sanya wadannan marasa lafiya cikin gwajin bazuwar, yanzu za mu sami amsa dalla-dalla game da tasirin plasma convalescent. "
Horby kara da cewa UK farfadowa da na'ura yanzu ya kaddamar da wani bazuwar fitina na convalescent jini amma ba ya sa ran sakamakon ya zama a shirye har sai daga baya wannan shekara.
Masar ta fara rajistar bayanan masu kada kuri'a a kasashen waje don zaben 'yan majalisar dattijai
Hukumar Zabe Mai Zaman Kanta ta Kasa (NEA) a ranar Asabar ta fara rajistar bayanan masu jefa kuri’a a cikin jirgin don fara jefa kuri’unsu a zaben sanata da za a gudanar a ranar 9 da 10 ga watan Agusta, kamar yadda shafin yanar gizon NEA ya ruwaito.
