Kansas City magajin garin maraba da gwamnatin taimako a warware kisan kai, amma damuwa game da trump ta muradi
Kansas City Magajin Quinton Lucas tambaye a ranar Lahadi Shugaba Trump muradi na aika jamiái tarayya a Amurka birane - ya ce, yayin da zai maraba da taimako a warware kashe kashe a tsakiyar yammacin birnin, yana ganin matakin zai iya zama mafi game da buoying trump ta sake zaben chances.
Lucas, a Democrat, ya ce a kan "Fox News Lahadi" na kwanan nan zanga-zanga a kan launin fata rashin daidaito da kuma 'yan sanda zalunci.
"Wannan ba haka lamarin yake a Kansas City. Mun yi shekara-kan-shekara qara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kan shi ne ainihin share wasu daga cikin unsolved kisan."
Lucas kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi kokarin samun pinpointed da niyya mayar da hankali a kan warware kisan...Ina ganin idan ka saurari 'yan kalamai... muna farin ciki da yin aiki tare da tarayya jamiái a wata iyaka ikon yinsa."
Duk da cewa yana shirye ya sa jami'an gwamnatin tarayya su yi aiki tare da dokar gida, Lucas ya ce kalaman Trump - musamman bisa la'akari da takaddama game da dabarun da jami'an tarayya ke amfani da su a Portland, Ore., sun sa da yawa daga cikin 'yan asalinsa sun damu game da kasancewar jami'an tsaro a kan titunan birnin.
"Abin da ba mu bukatar shi ne mafi man fetur a kan wuta daga tarayya jamiái yi, ina ganin, mai ban sha'awa siyasa batun," ya ce.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa yana tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen magance tashe-tashen hankula na wasu laifuka - matakin da ke nuna fadada shigar White House cikin dokar ta-baci yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban "dokar da oda".
A "bincike" na jamiái sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da kuma sauran American birane ne wani ɓangare na Operation Legend - mai suna bayan 4-shekara LeGend Taliferro, wanda aka fatally harbe yayin barci a cikin wani Kansas City Apartment a karshen watan jiya.
Babban Lauya Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan yunkurin a watan Disamba ga birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da aka tura, da kuma wasu daga cikin dabarun su, sun haifar da damuwa tsakanin 'yan majalisun jihohi da na kananan hukumomi.
Wasu 'yan majalisar dokoki daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana kan gwamnatin Trump da ke tura jami'an zuwa garuruwansu, musamman ma bayan rahotannin da suka nuna cewa jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da ba a san ko su wanene ba sun tsare masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun tafi da su a cikin motocin da ba a san ko su wanene ba.
Portland da aka buga tare da kusa-kullum zanga-zanga da 'yan sanda zalunci da kuma tsarin wariyar launin fata tun mutuwar George Floyd yayin da a Minneapolis 'yan sanda a tsare a kan May 25.
Hukumomi sun kuma yi korafin cewa karuwar ta kara haifar da rikici ne kawai, kuma masana shari'a masu laifi sun ce kokarin da ake yi na kaucewa bayani saboda irin lokacin da Amurka ke ciki - tare da annoba, rashin aikin tarihi da kuma yawan tunani kan wariyar launin fata da yadda 'yan sanda ke kula da mutane masu launi.
AP ta caccaki sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany don bayanin "siyasa" - amma manema labarai sun ci gaba da yin tambayoyin siyasa - RT News Hausa
Jaridar The Associated Press ta zargi sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da damuwa da kafofin watsa labarai ta hanyar yin mata bayani a siyasance maimakon bayani - a fili ya manta da cewa manema labarai sun zabi tambayoyin.
An labarin Asabar da AP, most US news agency, ya ce White House labarai briefings iya zama "karye hadisin," kamar yadda McEnany ya sanya su "a streamlined, full-throated talla ga shugaban kasar ta sake zaben, a wuri domin kai hare-hare a kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma wani forum gwada haske a kan bayanai" game da abin da gwamnatin da aka yi.
Na karshe wadanda assertions ne indisputable, kamar yadda wuya wani sabon bayani da aka saukar a briefings.
Abin da AP kasa ambaci shi ne, da wuya wani sabon bayani ne a zahiri nemi a briefings.
Sau da yawa manema labarai suna amfani da masu latsa White House don jawo hankali ga kansu, wani nau'in zane-zane wanda Jim Acosta na CNN ya inganta.
Sun wuce da hankula husuma kafofin watsa labarai-gudanarwa dangantaka, maimaita juna a tambayar gotcha tambayoyi da nufin kawai impugning Shugaba Donald trump.
A wasu lokuta, suna mai da kansu labarai, kamar lokacin da jaridar CBS ta Weijia Jiang ta amsa "tambayar China" ta mayar da martani daga Trump ta hanyar yin alamar da ba ta dace ba game da wariyar launin fata: "Sir, me yasa kake cewa a gare ni musamman?"
A Yuli 6 briefing miƙa wani Firayim misali da cire haɗin kan yadda briefings sun daina zama tushen m bayanai ga Amirkawa.
Trump ya tweeted cewa da safe cewa NASCAR ta talabijin ratings aka ji rauni da wani ƙarya zargin da wata kiyayya laifi a kan direba Bubba Wallace da kuma ta yanke shawarar hana nuna Confederate flag a da abubuwan da suka faru.
Tsinkaya, mafi yawan tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet a matsayin rahoto bayan rahoto ya tambayi McEnany tambayoyi tsara don sa ta ta ta ce trump goyon bayan Confederate flag.
McEnany bai bayar da amsar manema labarai so - sauti cizo cewa zai cutar da trump - amma ta sau da yawa amsa da cewa shugaban kasar ba shan matsayi a kan Confederate flag kuma cewa gist da sako shi ne cewa NASCAR magoya aka kuskure da ake nuna a matsayin nuna wariyar launin fata.
The AP ce ta busa "exaspered" a lokacin briefing.
Labarin AP ya maimaita shafi na Washington Post op-ed a farkon wannan watan ta wakilin ABC News Jonathan Karl, wanda kuma shine shugaban kungiyar Ma'aikatan Fadar White House.
Karl bayar da hujjar, "mutunta gaskiya da kuma yin amfani da White House podium for zalla siyasa dalilai ne a keta na jama'a dogara."
Amma duk da haka McEnany ta sauri mayu da combative style sanya ta a gwarzo na wasu trump magoya bayan, tun da ta ba ta farko tattaunawa a kan May 1 bayan shan kan matsayin manema sakataren a watan Afrilu.
A pressers ya kasance ba a nan fiye da shekara guda kafin ta nada.
Kamar sauran bangarorin rayuwar siyasa a Washington, dangantakar sakataren yada labarai na White House da kafofin watsa labarai ta canza sosai a zamanin Trump.
Wannan canji ya zo daga garesu da predated McEnany ta zuwa.
A gasa tsohon sakataren yada labarai Sarah Huckabee Sanders da comedian Michelle Wolf a White House Correspondents "cin abincin dare a watan Afrilu 2018 ya haka mugun cewa ko da MSNBC rundunar Mika Brzezinski kira shi "deplorable."
AP White House rahoto Jill Colvin gaishe McEnany a ta farko briefing da tambaya, "Za ka jingina kada su yi ƙarya da mu daga cewa podium?"
Fox News siyasa Analyst Brit Hume, wani tsohon soja na fiye da 50 shekaru a aikin jarida wanda yana da 1989-1996 stint a matsayin ABC ta babban White House wakilinmu, ya ce manema labarai a yau nuna "m hali" a cikin briefing dakin saboda su raini trump.
Shi ne saboda su anti-Trump mayar da hankali, ya ce wannan mako a kan Fox ta Tucker Carlson Yau da dare shirin, 'yan jarida suna sakaci don tara manufofin labarai.
"Ba kawai wasan gotcha ba ne," in ji Hume game da manufar da aka yi nufi da masu latsawa.
"Ba wai kawai yunkurin kunyata wani jami'in jama'a ba ne, don cire bayanai ne."
