Kudlow ya ce dokar kara kuzari ta coronavirus ta gaba za ta hada da karin dubawa, tsawaita dakunan gwaje-gwaje kan fitarwa
Larry Kudlow mai ba da shawara kan tattalin arziki na White House ya yi alkawarin a ranar Lahadi cewa gwamnatin tarayya za ta tsawaita dakin gwaje-gwaje a kan fitar da kuma aika da wani zagaye na cak a matsayin wani ɓangare na gaba coronavirus kara kuzari kunshin.
Kudlow ta comments zo bayan mako guda inda White House ta fatan ga albashi haraji rage da aka harbe saukar da Congress.
Kudlow ya ce a kan CNN ta "State of the Union."
"Amma, ya zama kamar yadda ya iya, a siyasance, ba ya aiki."
