Mnuchin ce sabon lissafin zai samar da ƙarin rashin aikin yi amfanin, amma lura da cewa shi zai zama kasa da biya bayar a karkashin CARES dokar.
Ya ce wasu ma'aikata suna tattara fiye da yadda suka samu a kan aiki.
