Mutanen Espanya jami'an sun kuma yi gargadin a karo na biyu kalaman iya sananne kamar yadda manyan birane sun gani lokuta karuwa.
Airlines ciki har da British Airways sun soki sabon matakan a matsayin "duk da haka wani bugun" ga 'yan hutu na Birtaniya.
Mutane a halin yanzu a kan hutu a Spain da aka shawarci da Ma'aikatar sufuri da su bi dokokin gida, koma gida kamar yadda na al'ada, da kuma duba Ofishin Harkokin Waje ta tafiya shawara website don ƙarin bayani.
Ofishin Harkokin Waje yana ba da shawara game da duk amma tafiye-tafiye masu mahimmanci zuwa babban yankin Spain, duk da haka matakan keɓancewa sun shafi waɗanda suka dawo daga babban yankin Spain, Canary Islands da Balearic Islands, kamar Majorca da Ibiza.
Harkokin waje Office shawara yana ramifications for tafiya inshora.
Daga cikin wadanda sabuwar ka'idojin ta shafa akwai Sakataren sufuri Grant Shapps, wanda ya fara hutunsa a Spain a ranar Asabar.
Ana sa ran zai ci gaba da tafiya kamar yadda ya shirya da kuma ware bisa ga shiriya a kan ya dawo.
An fara gabatar da matakan kebewa ga matafiya na Burtaniya a farkon Yuni.
Amma bayan matsin lamba daga masana'antun jiragen sama da na tafiye-tafiye, gwamnati da gwamnatocin da suka bijire sun buga jerin sunayen kasashen da ba a bin ka'idodin ba.
Kamfanin jiragen sama na British Airways ya ce "abin takaici ne" game da sabbin sauye-sauye na shawarwarin tafiye-tafiyen gwamnati da dokoki, kodayake kamfanin jirgin saman ya ce jiragensa suna ci gaba da aiki.
Ya ce matakin "ya jefa dubban 'yan Burtaniya' shirin tafiye-tafiye cikin rudani."
The Airport aiki Association ce sabon matakan zai "m lalata abin da yake riga a m sake kunnawa na jirgin sama kansu wanda ya ci gaba da fuskantar babbar kalubale a cikin tarihi."
The UK ta babbar yawon shakatawa sadarwarka, Tui, soke ta flights saboda tashi zuwa babban yankin kasar Spain da Canary Islands a ranar Lahadi.
Customers a halin yanzu a kan hutu za su iya komawa a kan su nufi jirgin gida.
Koyaya, kamfanin jirgin sama na EasyJet ya ce "ya ɓace" kuma zai yi aiki da cikakken tsari a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
"Abokan ciniki da suka daina so su yi tafiya za su iya canja wurin su flights ba tare da wani canji fee ko sami wani baucan ga darajar da booking," kamfanin ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa.
Wani mai magana da yawun kungiyar jami'an kula da tafiye-tafiye na Birtaniya (Abta) ya ce sauye-sauyen da gwamnati ta yi na kebewa "abin takaici ne."
"Muna ba da shawarar gwamnati ta yi la'akari da dage ka'idojin kebe jiragen sama zuwa wasu yankuna da ke da karancin kamuwa da cuta, ko zuwa wurare kamar tsibirin Balearic ko Kanaries - wanda ya bambanta da yankin Spain - don kauce wa ƙarin lalacewar masana'antun yawon shakatawa na Burtaniya," in ji shi.
Ya zuwa yanzu Spain ta ga mutuwar coronavirus sama da 28,000.
A ranar Alhamis, ta ga babbar karuwa ta yau da kullun a kamuwa da cuta tun lokacin da dokar kulle ta ƙare.
Catalonia ya zama latest yankin to crack saukar a kan nightlife.
Yankin arewa maso gabas mai arziki, wanda gida ne ga Barcelona, ya umarci duk wuraren shakatawa na dare su rufe na tsawon makonni biyu kuma su sanya dokar hana fita a tsakar dare a kan mashaya a mafi girman yankin Barcelona.
Guy Hedgecoe na BBC a Madrid ya ce yaduwar cutar a tsakanin matasa wata damuwa ce ta musamman, saboda suna tattarawa da yawa a cikin birane da daddare.
Faransa ta gargadi 'yan kasarta da kada su tafi Catalonia yayin da Norway ta ce za ta fara killace mutanen da suka zo daga Spain.
Gwamnatin tana kira ga ma'aikata da su zama "fahimtar wadanda suka dawo daga Spain wadanda a yanzu za su bukaci killace kansu."
Amma sakataren gida na kungiyar kwadago Nick Thomas-Symonds ya yi kira ga gwamnati da ta bayyana dalla-dalla yadda za ta tallafa wa wadanda abin ya shafa, ya kara da cewa labarin zai zama "mai zurfi game da iyalan da aka kama a Spain ko kuma suke shirin tafiya."
Scottish First Minister Nicola Sturgeon tweeted cewa an yanke shawarar bayan nazarin latest data farkon a ranar Asabar.
"Wannan yana karfafa batun cewa wadannan al'amura za su iya canzawa a gajere don haka shawarata ita ce a mai da hankali game da tafiye-tafiye na kasashen waje da ba su da muhimmanci," in ji ta.
John Blackmore, daga Hampshire, shi ne saboda tashi fita zuwa iyalinsa a Spain tare da matarsa da kuma biyu kananan yara.
Amma sabbin ka'idojin suna nufin dole ne ya soke, saboda tsoron shugaban aikinsa na matarsa ba zai iya saukar da ita ba don daukar karin makonni biyu don keɓewa bayan dawowar su.
Ya ce yana tsammanin da alama ba za su sami biyan kuɗi ba don jirgin, saboda ba a soke shi ba.
"Na fatattakakkun," ya shaida wa BBC.
"Ina da iyali a Spain waɗanda ba su ga jikokinsu kawai ba tun daga Kirsimeti."
Lois Stothard, daga South Yorkshire, ya shaida wa BBC cewa ta kama wani biki zuwa Seville a matsayin abin mamaki ga saurayinta 30th birthday - saboda tashi daga a ranar Lahadi da safe - amma yanzu ji cewa ba za ta iya tafiya.
"Ni ma'aikaciyar keywork ce - ni malama ce - kuma saurayina yana da alkawurran aiki don haka ba za mu iya kebewa na tsawon kwanaki 14 ba idan muka dawo," in ji ta.
"Ba za mu iya samun wani kudi da baya da kuma canza kamfanin so ninki biyu abin da na riga na biya a kudade.
Na yi matukar baƙin ciki da kuma kau da kai kamar yadda muke cushe da kuma shirye su tafi. "
Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi "kudaden kuɗi ne a kan matsalar kuma rufe Amurka"
Washington - Sanatan jam'iyyar Republican Ted Cruz na Texas ya zargi kakakin majalisar wakilai Nancy Pelosi da 'yan Democrat da tura kunshin kayan agaji na coronavirus wanda ke mayar da hankali kan "raba tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka" yayin da ake ci gaba da tattaunawa kan mataki na gaba.
A wata hira da ya yi da "Face the Nation" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar na fuskantar rikice-rikice guda biyu a lokaci guda: annobar duniya da ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane fiye da 600,000 a duk duniya da kuma "bala'in tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya bayyana a kan "Face the Nation" a gaban sanatan, "ba a mayar da hankali a kan wadanda."
"Ta manufofin da ake shoveling tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe America saukar," da Texas Republican ce.
"Kuma musamman, ka dubi dala tiriliyan 3 lissafin da ta ke kokarin tura, yana da kawai shoveling kudi ta abokai da ba a zahiri warware matsalar. Our haƙiƙa ya kamata Amurkawa son komawa bakin aiki. Suna so su iya azurta iyalinsu."
‘Yan Republican na Majalisar Dattawa da Fadar White House sun shafe makon da ya gabata suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan kashi na hudu na amsar coronavirus, wanda suke sa ran zai kashe dala tiriliyan 1.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma’aikatan Fadar White House Mark Meadows da Sakataren Baitulmali Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill don karin tattaunawa da ma’aikatan Majalisar Dattawa, kuma Mnuchin ya fada wa Fox News a cikin wata hira a ranar Lahadi za a bayyana cikakken bayanin da shugaban masu rinjaye na Majalisar Dattawa Mitch McConnell ya yi a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi ci wa 'yan majalisa tuwo a kwarya - wanda kuma batu ne na jayayya tsakanin 'yan jam'iyyar Republican da Democrats - shi ne batun rashin aikin yi da ya kare, wanda ya fara karewa a karshen mako.
Duk da yake 'yan Democrat suna son "lokaci na hudu" coronavirus kunshin don ci gaba da goyon baya ga amfanin, Republican suna kira ga shi da za a pared baya da kuma jayayya wasu Amirkawa yi mafi daga rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suka yi a sakamakon.
Cruz ya ce fiye da rabin Amurkawa da ke samun ingantattun fa'idodin rashin aikin yi ana biyansu fiye da lokacin da suke aiki kuma ya ce yana magana ne da kananan 'yan kasuwa a Texas wadanda ke fama da matsala wajen gyara ma'aikata.
"Tabbas, ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya tana biyansu, a wasu lokuta, sau biyu kudin da za su zauna a gida," in ji shi.
Cruz ya ce Majalisa kamata a mayar da hankali a kan wucewa a dawo da lissafin cewa zai sa shi sauki ga Amirkawa komawa bakin aiki da sassauta haraji da ka'idoji a kan kananan harkokin kasuwanci: "maimakon kawai shoveling tiriliyoyin fitar da kofa, a dawo da lissafin zai dakatar da albashi haraji, wanda zai ba shi albashi sama ga kowa da kowa a Amurka wanda ke aiki. Wannan zahiri samun mutane a mayar da aiki,"In ji shi.
Shugaba Trump ya bukaci a makon da ya gabata kunshin taimakon na gaba ya hada da rage harajin albashi, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai kasance cikin dokokin ba, saboda shawarar ba ta da lafiya a tsakanin 'yan Republican.
Mr. trump yarda da albashi haraji yanke zai zama ba daga na gaba lissafin amma nemi fil da laifi a kan Democrats.
Cruz, wanda a makon da ya gabata ya yi watsi da kudin na gaba kunshin, ya ce Lahadi ya ba a kan jirgin tare da awo daga 'yan'uwansa majalisar dattijai Republican.
Amma kuma ya soki dokar dala tiriliyan 3 da majalisar da Democrat ke iko da ita a watan Mayu, ya kuma zargi abokan adawarsa na siyasa da aikata wani mataki da ke lalata shugaban kasar gabanin zaben watan Nuwamba da gangan.
"The kawai haƙiƙa Democrats da shi ne ya kayar da Donald trump, kuma suka yi cynically yanke shawarar hanya mafi kyau da za a kayar da Donald trump aka rufe kowane kasuwanci a Amurka, rufe kowane makaranta a Amurka," ya ce.
"Kun sani, Nancy Pelosi tana magana game da maza da mata masu aiki. Abin da take ba da shawara shi ne kiyaye maza da mata masu aiki daga aiki."
Shirin Bada Tukuici Don Adalci - Wadanda Ake Nema Don Laifin Ta’addanci - Rahul Gandhi
Rahul Gandhi ya wallafa wani bidiyo a yau inda ya yi yunkurin wayar da kan jama’a a kan BJP kan abubuwan da suka faru a Rajasthan.
Ta hanyar amfani da hashtag "SpeakUpForDemocracy," ya Hindia post ya bukaci mutane da su "Hadin kai da kuma tayar da muryarmu ga dimokuradiyya."
Majalisar tana shirin gudanar da zanga-zanga a kasar a ranar Litinin game da halin da ake ciki a Rajasthan, inda gwamnatin Ashok Gehlot ke fama da tsira.
Yayin da jam'iyyar ta ce za a gudanar da zanga-zanga a wajen Rashtrapati Bhavan, gidan shugaban kasar Ram Nath Kovind.
A cikin bidiyon, Majalisa ta zargi BJP da "karya kundin tsarin mulki da rushe dimokuradiyya" yayin da kasar baki daya ke yaki da coronavirus.
Ya yi haka a Madhya Pradesh, Majalisa ce.
"Muna bukatar a nan da nan kira wani taro zaman wanda yake a cikin mu tsarin mulki hakkoki," jam'iyyar ce a cikin video.
Rajasthan Gwamna Kalraj Mishra ya juya baya daya shawara don fara wani taro zaman.
Na biyu shi ne wanda aka sallama a yau wanda ya ce ya na nazarin.
Gwamnatin Mr Gehlot ta kasance cikin mawuyacin hali bayan da mataimakinsa Sachin Pilot ya juya wa 'yan tawaye tare da rukunin MLAs da ke goyon bayansa.
Jam'iyyar ba ta iya dakatar da 'yan tawayen don saukar da alamar mafi rinjaye a cikin taron ba.
Mr Pilot - wanda aka kwace daga posts a cikin jam'iyyar da kuma gwamnati - An bai wa wucin gadi taimako daga rashin cancantar da Rajasthan High Court, wanda gudanar da cewa Kakakin ba zai iya daukar wani mataki har sai da ya fi girma tsarin mulki tambaya game da ikonsa da aka yanke shawarar.
Kotun Koli za ta dauki wannan tambayar gobe, wanda kuma zai yanke hukunci ko kotu za ta iya tsoma baki cikin hukuncin Kakakin.
The Congress tsaye daya kawai da mafi rinjaye alama a cikin 200-member taron.
Team Pilot ikirarin da goyon bayan 30 MLAs, amma ya zuwa yanzu, da shaida nuna wa kawai 19.
BJP yana da 72 kuma gami da masoya da masu zaman kansu, yana tsaye a 97.
Idan kotu ta yanke shawarar goyon bayan Mr Pilot, Majalisa za ta iya rasa na biyu daga cikin gwamnatoci uku da ta kafa a jihohin da ke kusa da ita biyo bayan zaben jama'a na 2018.
A watan Maris, shi rasa Kamal Nath-kai gwamnati a Madhya Pradesh bayan Jyotiraditya Scindia shiga BJP tare da 22 daga cikin MLAs.
An kama wasu jami'an 'yan sanda a Kenya bayan sun yi harbi a Garissa
An kama wasu jami’an ‘yan sanda biyu a Kenya dangane da harbin da aka yi inda aka kashe mutane biyu.
Wannan harbin ya faru ne a kasuwar Soko Ng’ombe da ke karamar hukumar Garissa ta gabas a ranar Asabar, a lokacin da ake zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewa da kama wani mutum da ake zargi da laifin kisan kai.
Latsa wannan domin samun sabuwar manhajar labarai ta Legit.ng Hausa a wayar ku ta hannu:
Hukumar 'yan sanda ta Kenya ta kaddamar da bincike game da harbe-harben.
Zai hada da "bincike na bincike" na bindigogin jami'an.
Garissa MP Aden Duale kira mutuwar "heinous" da kuma Allah wadai da "'yan sanda zalunci" a cikin wata sanarwa posted to Facebook.
Masu kamfen sun tayar da damuwa game da 'yan sanda a lokacin annobar.
A cewar kungiyar kare hakkin bil'adama ta Amnesty International, jami'an Kenya sun kashe mutane 21 tun daga watan Maris saboda rashin bin matakan rigakafin cutar coronavirus kamar dokar hana fita da sanya takunkumin rufe fuska.
A farkon wannan watan 'yan sanda a Nairobi babban birnin kasar sun harba hayaki mai sa hawaye sannan kuma sun kama wasu masu zanga-zanga da ke gudanar da zanga-zangar shekara-shekara ta Saba Saba - wani taron zanga-zangar da aka fara shekaru 30 da suka gabata kan gwamnatin shugaba Daniel arap Moi na wancan lokacin.
Masu aiko da rahotanni sun ce an ba taron na bana karin kuzari saboda fushi kan fashe-fashe da 'yan sanda suka yi a lokacin dokar kulle ta Covid-19.
Shivraj Singh Chouhan A Gwajin Gwajin Cutar Covid
Madhya Pradesh Babban Ministan kasar Shivraj Singh Chouhan, wanda a ranar Asabar ya tabbatar da cewa ya kamu da COVID-19, ya yi tweeted Lahadi da safe ya ce shi ne "lafiya" da kuma bayar da yabo ga gaba-line ma'aikata a yaki da korona.
Babban Ministan ya kuma maimaita gargadinsa daga jiya, lokacin da ya bukaci mutane da su bi ka'idoji, kamar nisantar jama'a da amfani da abin rufe fuska.
"Ina da kyau, abokaina. Keɓewar mayaƙan coronavirus, waɗanda suka sadaukar da rayukansu ba tare da son kai ba, abin yabo ne. Ina yi wa dukkan mayaƙan coronavirus na jihar wa'azi," Mr Chouhan ya tweeted daga asibitin Bhopal na Chirayu, inda aka kwantar da shi a jiya.
"Ku nisanci mita biyu, ku wanke hannuwanku akai-akai kuma ku sanya abin rufe fuska - wadannan su ne manyan makaman da muke da su don guje wa coronavirus. Ina kira ga dukkan mutane da su yi amfani da wadannan makamai don kanku da masoyanku," in ji shi.
"Dukanku ku yi hankali, ku zauna lafiya da lafiya. Wannan shi ne abin da na yi addu'a ga Allah," Mr Chouhan ya kara da cewa.
A ranar Asabar Mr Chouhan ya yi tweeted cewa ya kamu da cutar duk da kokarin da ya yi don kauce wa kamuwa da cutar kuma ya yi gargadin cewa "kawai dan rashin kula yana kiran coronavirus."
Da yake magana da safiyar yau Mr Chouhan ya ce duk da barazanar kamuwa da cutar babu "babu bukatar jin tsoro" kuma ya bukaci wadanda ke nuna alamun cutar da su yi gwaji da kansu.
"Idan kun kamu da cutar, babu bukatar ku ji tsoro. Kada ku ɓoye alamun cutar amma ku gaya wa likitoci nan da nan, don haka za a iya fara magani. Magani na lokaci zai sa ku lafiya," in ji shi.
Madhya Pradesh tana da kusan 27,000 masu kamuwa da COVID-19, wanda sama da 7,600 ke aiki kuma 799 sune mutuwar da ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar.
Indiya ta samu karuwar masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin makonnin da suka gabata, inda aka gano sama da sabbin mutane 45,000 a kowace rana tun daga 23 ga Yuli.
Adadin wadanda aka tabbatar sun kamu da cutar coronavirus yana gabatowa da sauri 14 lakh; daga cikin wadannan fiye da 4.67 lakh sune masu aiki kuma sama da 32,000 sune mutuwa da ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar.
Karuwar lamura, daidai da tsagaita shakatawa na ka'idojin kulle a yankunan da ba a kiyayewa ba na kasar, ya fitar da Indiya zuwa na uku a jerin al'ummomin da abin ya fi shafa.
Kawai Amurka (41.78 lakh lokuta) da Brazil (23.94 lakh lokuta) ne mafi muni kashe.
Tunisia ministan cikin gida mai suna sabon PM, ya kafa gwamnati a cikin wata guda
An nada Hichem Mechichi ministan harkokin cikin gida na Tunisia don ya kafa gwamnati ta gaba, in ji ofishin shugaban kasar, a yayin rikicin siyasa tsakanin manyan jam'iyyu a Arewacin Afirka.
Lauyan mai shekaru 46 ya yi nasara a kan Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya yi murabus a matsayin firayim minista a farkon wannan watan.
Amma Mechichi bai kasance daya daga cikin sunayen da jam'iyyun siyasa suka gabatar wa Shugaba Kais Saied ba.
A wata sanarwa bayan sanarwar da ya fitar ranar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce "zai yi aiki don kafa gwamnatin da za ta dace da tsammanin duk 'yan Tunisiya."
Tunisia da aka yaba a matsayin rare nasara labarin for dimokuradiyya miƙa mulki bayan Arab Spring yankin tashin hankali tartsatsi ta haifar da ta 2011 juyin juya halin.
Amma shugabanninta sun yi gwagwarmaya don biyan bukatun al'ummar Tunisiya kuma tattalin arzikin da ya riga ya lalace sakamakon rufe iyakokin kasar saboda annobar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe kusan mutane 50 kuma ta kamu da cutar fiye da 1,400 a Tunisia.
Kazalika, kasancewa ministan cikin gida a cikin gwamnati mai barin gado, Mechichi ya kasance mai ba da shawara ga Shugaba Saied, da ke tafiyar da al'amura na shari'a.
Ya kasance a baya shugaban ma'aikata a ma'aikatar sufuri da kuma aiki a ma'aikatar harkokin jama'a.
A halin yanzu dai yana da wata guda da zai kafa gwamnati, wacce a wannan lokacin za ta fuskanci kuri'ar amincewa ta majalisa sannan kuma za ta bukaci gagarumin rinjaye da za ta yi nasara.
Kasawa cewa, majalisar dokoki za a rushe da kuma sabon zaben da za a gudanar a cikin watanni uku.
A zaben karshe da aka gudanar a watan Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ta hau kan gaba amma ta fadi kasa da mafi yawa kuma daga bisani ta amince ta shiga gwamnatin hadin gwiwa.
Fakhfakh ta yi murabus a ranar 15 ga watan Yuli, bayan kasa da watanni biyar a kan karagar mulki, barazanar sabon siyasa deadlock a cikin al'umma, kamar yadda fama da tattalin arziki fallout na annobar.
The murabusation zurfafa siyasa muhawara tare da Ennahdha kan zargin da Fakhfakh na rikice-rikice na ban sha'awa.
Dangantaka tsakanin shugaban mai barin gado mai shekaru 47 da Ennahdha ta yi tsami tun daga zaben majalisar dokoki na watan Oktoba.
Fakhfakh ya sauka a wannan rana da jam'iyyar ta shigar da kara ba tare da amincewa da shi ba.
Ennahdha ya farko zabi mai zaman kanta ga firaministan kasar, amma ya kasa lashe goyon bayan majalisar dokoki, manyan shugaban kasar don sunan tsohon ministan kudi Fakhfakh ga post.
A karshe dai Ennahdha ya amince da shiga cikin gwamnatin hadin gwuiwa.
Mota tana ratsa jama'a, an harbe mai zanga-zanga a Colorado
AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Wata mota ta bi ta cikin jama'a kuma an harbe wani mai zanga-zanga a unguwar Denver da ke unguwar Aurora a lokacin zanga-zangar nuna rashin adalci na launin fata.
Hukumar 'yan sanda ta Aurora ta wallafa a shafinta na Twitter cewa masu zanga-zanga suna tafiya a kan hanyar 225 Asabar lokacin da wata mota ta ratsa.
'Yan sanda sun ce wani mai zanga-zanga ya harba makami, inda ya buge akalla mutum daya da aka kai shi asibiti cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Hukumomi sun ce an tuka motar kuma suna gudanar da bincike.
Masu zanga-zangar sun kuma karya tagogi zuwa farfajiyar kuma an fara wuta a wani ofishi, in ji 'yan sanda.
An ayyana wani taron da bai dace ba kuma 'yan sanda sun umarci masu zanga-zanga su bar yankin, in ji hukumomi.
Tashin hankali da aka kara a kwanan nan zanga-zangar nuna wariyar launin fata rashin adalci tun tarayya jami'an da aka aika zuwa kashe zanga-zanga a Portland, Oregon.
'Yan sanda ayyana wani tarzoma a Seattle a ranar Asabar.
Zanga-zangar da ta faru a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu, mutuwar George Floyd, wani bakar fata a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan wani jami'in farin kaya ya rike shi a kasa tare da gwiwa a wuyansa, sun kuma nuna wasu shari'o'in tashin hankali na 'yan sanda.
A jihar Colorado, masu zanga-zanga sun jawo hankali ga mutuwar Iliya McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka dakatar yayin da yake tafiya a kan titin Aurora a watan Agustan 2019 bayan wani mai kira 911 ya ruwaito shi a matsayin mai tuhuma.
'Yan sanda sanya shi a cikin wani chokehold, da kuma paramedics gudanar 500 milligrams na ketamine, a sedative, don kwantar da shi.
Ya shiga bugun zuciya, daga baya aka ayyana kwakwalwa matattu da kuma kawar da goyon bayan rayuwa.
Shahararren bayyananne Lake Tahoe an ƙazantar da sauyin yanayi
Kudancin Tafkin Tahoe, California - Duk da cutar, har ma a ranar mako, mutane har yanzu suna taron Pope Beach a Tafkin Tahoe.
"Ina son zango da ciwon bike tafiya da kuma faruwa iyo a Lake," ya ce wata yarinya mai suna Dakota.
"Wannan wani abu ne mai kyau kowa yana so ya ziyarci," in ji Emerica Benitas.
